Package: screenmill.grid
Type: Package
Title: screenmill grid manipulation functions
Version: 0.1.7
Authors@R: c(
    person("Robert", "Reid", email = "rr381@cumc.columbia.edu", role = c("aut","cre")),
    person("Eric", "Bryant", email = "eeb2139@columbia.edu", role = c("aut")))
Maintainer: 'Robert Reid' <rr381@cumc.columbia.edu>
Description: Collection of functions to modify colony grids in screenmill data.
    Helps to fix calibration errors for incorrectly cropped plates by moving
    or resizing crop values or modifying individual grid positions
